*&quot;A Good Baby&quot; (1989)
*&quot;Who Goes There&quot; (1998)
*&quot;The Fall of Gravity&quot; (2000)
*&quot;The Beautiful Wife&quot; (2005)

===Short story collections===
Approximately 350 short stories published.
