===Hahn–Banach theorem for seminorms===

Seminorms offer a particularly clean formulation of the Hahn–Banach theorem: 
:If formula_91 is a vector subspace of a seminormed space formula_13 and if formula_43 is a continuous linear functional on formula_94 then formula_43 may be extended to a continuous linear functional formula_96 on formula_1 that has the same norm as formula_98

