====Stronger, weaker, and equivalent seminorms====

The notions of stronger and weaker seminorms are akin to the notions of stronger and weaker norms. If formula_11 and formula_73 are seminorms on formula_24 then we say that formula_73 is than formula_11 and that formula_11 is than formula_73 if any of the following equivalent conditions holds:

# The topology on formula_1 induced by formula_73 is finer than the topology induced by formula_30
